# Create a Meta App at https://developers.facebook.com/apps, add the "Facebook Login for Business"
# product, and add yourself (and any client accounts) as an Admin/Developer/Tester on the app.
# This app can stay in Development Mode — no App Review is needed to connect Pages you or your
# testers administer.
#
# Under Facebook Login > Settings > Valid OAuth Redirect URIs, add exactly:
#   https://127.0.0.1:53682/callback
# (Meta requires HTTPS for every redirect URI, including loopback ones — AutoPost's local
# callback server serves HTTPS with a self-signed cert for this, and always binds this
# fixed port. Your browser will show a one-time certificate warning on each connect;
# that's expected for a local, non-public endpoint — click through it.)
META_APP_ID=
META_APP_SECRET=
